content.title: The New York Times - Breaking News, US News, World News and Videos
content.metaDescription: Live news, investigations, opinion, photos and video by the journalists of The New York Times from more than 150 countries around the world. Subscribe for coverage of U.S. and international news, politics, business, technology, science, health, arts, sports and more.

# New York Times - Top Stories
[Trump Considers Overhaul of Refugee System That Would Favor White People](https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/15/us/politics/trump-refugee-white-people.html)The proposals would transform a program aimed at helping the most vulnerable people in the world into one that gives preference to mostly white people.
6 min read
